name: WichitaGuide
0:
”Alexa, ask wichita guide for the top five things to do”
”Where should I go”
”Tell me the local news”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wichita guide
des:
Visiting Wichita for the first time or just looking for new adventures to try? Either way, you can keep up to date with news and attractions around the city by asking Alexa.
You can ask: what are the top fives things to do, tell me a good attraction, what is the local news, or tell me some facts about Wichita.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
